data.description: This EXCEPTIONAL home is ready for you to MOVE right in! The beautiful CURB APPEAL will catch your attention but the INVITING FLOOR PLAN will make you feel right at home! The SEPARATE DINING ROOM is ready for special dinners & the kitchen is a dream. You’ll love the STAINLESS STEEL appliances & ample STORAGE will hold all your gadgets. Look at this cozy SUNROOM! What a great spot for coffee & a good book. The primary suite is a true retreat! A spa-like bath with a GARDEN TUB, SEPARATE VANITIES & SEPARATE SHOWER will cater to your every need. THREE additional bedrooms & a FULL BATH are perfect for CHILDREN, GUEST or HOME OFFICE. Upstairs is a huge GAME ROOM! You’ll have endless options for entertainment & relaxation. Finally…the PRIVATE backyard! Add a fire pit, roast marshmallows & have great conversations with friends! The MATURE greenery throughout the neighborhood, LOCAL small BUSINESSES & SHOPPING will satisfy all your family's needs! All it needs is YOU. Make your OFFER today!
